# 🎮 2D Game Project - Treasure Runner

A simple but engaging **2D platformer adventure game** built using Unity.  
Explore levels, avoid traps, jump over lava, and reach the treasure!

---

## 🧩 About the Game

This is a 2D platformer game where the player must:
- Collect items
- Avoid lava and traps
- Use moving platforms
- Reach the final treasure to complete the level

The game is developed using **Unity Engine (Unity 6.3)**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎮 Smooth player movement
- 🧱 Multiple levels
- 🔥 Lava & trap system
- 🪜 Moving platforms
- 💀 Checkpoint system
- 🎯 Win / Game Over system
- 🔊 Sound effects (if added)
- 📱 Mobile-friendly controls

---

## 🎮 Controls

### Keyboard (PC)
- ⬅️ Move Left
- ➡️ Move Right
- ⬆️ Jump
- 🔄 Restart Level

### Mobile (if available)
- On-screen buttons for movement and jump

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- 🎯 Unity 6.3
- 💻 C# scripting
- 🎨 Unity 2D Sprite system
- 🧠 Physics-based movement

